<L>__{exterior van day}
<A>__{the van is driven by kathy, sharon's brother's wife. beside her in a car seat is larry, jr., four years old. sharon comes to the rolled down window on the driver's side. she has a warm smile for kathy and the child. kathy smiles, too.}
<C>__{kathy}
